Sentencas: Ni-Al2O3 cermet supported tubular solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with different cathodes were fabricated by thermal spraying.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The anode, electrolyte and cathode were deposited by atmospheric plasma spraying (APS) aimed at reducing the manufacturing cost of SOFCs.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Three porous composite cathodes of lanthanum strontium manganite (LSM) and yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ), lanthanum strontium cobalt oxide (LSC) and YSZ, LSC and scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) were prepared to investigate influence of cathode constitutions on the cell's performance.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrode polarization can be improved through using a composite cathode.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the cell with APS YSZ electrolyte and LSC/ScSZ composite cathode is increased about 12% than pure LSM cathode.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The maximum output power density of the cell with APS ScSZ electrolyte and LSC/ScSZ composite cathode reaches 1.0 W/cm(2) at 1000 degrees C.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The further optimization of the performance of plasma-sprayed composite cathode can be made through improving the interface contact between YSZ electrolyte and composite cathode.
Titulo: Influence of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed Composite Cathode on the Performance of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
